Package: translateVTT
Type: Package
Title: Automatically translate VTT files
Version: 1.0.1.9000
Author: Vladimir Zhbanko
Maintainer: Vladimir Zhbanko <vladimir.zhbanko@gmail.com>
Description: Facilitate automated translation of files with a complex structure.
    Imports user files from a specified directory. Extracts text with closed captions,
    Sends this text to Google Translate API and retrieves back the
    translation. Original file structure will be restored.
    Provides facility to encrypt API keys
Depends:
    R (>= 3.4.3)
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports:
    tibble,
    tidyverse,
    translateR (>= 1.0),
    utils
RoxygenNote: 6.1.1
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Suggests: 
    testthat (>= 2.1.0)
